    "description": "Request collection for testing the Local Services Platform API.\n\nTo use this collection, set the following collection variables:\n- `gateway_url` → http://localhost:8072\n- `access_token` → JWT Bearer token from Keycloak\n- `keycloak_api_key` → Keycloak API key value (X-Keycloak-API-Key)\n\nServices running locally:\n- Gateway:         http://localhost:8072\n- User Service:    http://localhost:8080\n- Booking Service: http://localhost:8090\n- Offer Service:   http://localhost:9000\n- Keycloak:        http://localhost:7080",
